OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,FOceanGate's Titan submersible
OL,7,Fexpedition was "critically flawed" and
OL,8,Fits implosion "preventable", a US
OL,9,FCoast Guard investigation report has
OL,10,Fconcluded.
OL,12,FFive people ` including British
OL,13,Fadventurer Hamish Harding and father
OL,14,Fand son Shahzada and Suleman Dawood -
OL,15,Fdied on the maiden voyage of the
OL,16,Fsubmarine in June 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
