OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,FThe chief executive of tour operator
OL,7,FOceanGate Expeditions, Stockton Rush,
OL,8,Fand Titanic historian and French
OL,9,Fnational Paul-Henri Nargeolet, were
OL,10,Falso killed in the incident.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, the US Coast Guard Marine
OL,13,FBoard of Investigation (MBI) released
OL,14,Fa 335-page report investigating the
OL,15,Fevents leading up to and during the
OL,16,Fill-fated expedition to the wreckage
OL,17,Fof the Titanic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
