OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,FIt highlighted several key safety
OL,7,Ffailings and made 17 recommendations
OL,8,Fto improve maritime safety and prevent
OL,9,Ffuture incidents from occurring.
OL,11,FThe report criticised OceanGate's
OL,12,Fdesign and testing processes and the
OL,13,Fconcluded the accident occurred in
OL,14,Fpart due to a failure "to properly
OL,15,Finvestigate and address known hull
OL,16,Fanomalies" following an earlier
OL,17,Fexpedition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
