OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,FIt also said OceanGate had a "toxic
OL,7,Fworkplace environment" and used the
OL,8,F"looming threat of being fired" to
OL,9,Fprevent staff from coming forward with
OL,10,Fsafety concerns.
OL,12,FAccording to the report, a contractor
OL,13,Fhired by OceanGate in 2022 voiced
OL,14,F"numerous safety concerns" to a
OL,15,Fcompany director, before being told:
OL,16,F"You have a bad attitude, you don't
OL,17,Fhave an explorer mindset, you know,
OL,18,Fwe're innovative and we're cowboys,
OL,19,Fand a lot of people can't handle that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
