OL,6,FThe report read: "For several years
OL,7,Fpreceding the incident, OceanGate
OL,8,Fleveraged intimidation tactics,
OL,9,Fallowances for scientific operations,
OL,10,Fand the company's favourable
OL,11,Freputation to evade regulatory
OL,12,Fscrutiny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
