OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,F"By strategically creating and
OL,7,Fexploiting regulatory confusion and
OL,8,Foversight challenges, OceanGate was
OL,9,Fultimately able to operate Titan
OL,10,Fcompletely outside of the established
OL,11,Fdeep-sea protocols, which had
OL,12,Fhistorically contributed to a strong
OL,13,Fsafety record for commercial
OL,14,Fsubmersibles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
