OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F304A1754413221
OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,F"The lack of both third-party
OL,7,Foversight and experienced OceanGate
OL,8,Femployees on staff during their 2023
OL,9,FTitan operations allowed OceanGate's
OL,10,Fchief executive officer to completely
OL,11,Fignore vital inspections, data
OL,12,Fanalyses, and preventative maintenance
OL,13,Fprocedures, culminating in a
OL,14,Fcatastrophic event."
OL,16,FThe investigation concluded the
OL,17,F"sudden and catastrophic" implosion of
OL,18,Fthe Titan submersible was triggered by
OL,19,Fa loss of structural integrity in the
OL,20,Fcarbon fiber hull.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
