OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,FAll five individuals aboard killed
OL,7,Finstantly when the hull imploded,
OL,8,Fexposing them to approximately 4,930
OL,9,Fpounds per square inch of water
OL,10,Fpressure.
OL,12,FThe report said had OceanGate CEO
OL,13,FStockton Rush survived the incident he
OL,14,Fcould have faced criminal charges for
OL,15,Fnegligence.
OL,17,FThe loss of communications with the
OL,18,Fsubmersible mid-dive sparked a multi-
OL,19,Fnational search and rescue operation
OL,20,Finvolving ships and aircraft.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
