OL,6,FSpeaking following the report's
OL,7,Frelease, Jason Neubauer, who chaired
OL,8,Fthe investigation said: "This marine
OL,9,Fcasualty and the loss of five lives
OL,10,Fwas preventable.
OL,12,F"The two-year investigation has
OL,13,Fidentified multiple contributing
OL,14,Ffactors that led to this tragedy,
OL,15,Fproviding valuable lessons learned to
OL,16,Fprevent a future occurrence.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
