OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,F"There is a need for stronger
OL,7,Foversight and clear options for
OL,8,Foperators who are exploring new
OL,9,Fconcepts outside of the existing
OL,10,Fregulatory framework."
OL,12,FThe surviving family of British-
OL,13,FPakistani businessman Shahzada and his
OL,14,F19-year-old son Suleman, who both died
OL,15,Fin the implosion, released a statement
OL,16,Ffollowing the report's release calling
OL,17,Ffor tighter regulation in the industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
