OL,3,CTitan sub safety practices 'critically
OL,4,Cflawed' and implosion 'preventable'
OL,6,FIn it they said: "No report can alter
OL,7,Fthe heartbreaking outcome, nor fill
OL,8,Fthe immeasurable void left by two
OL,9,Fcherished members of our family.
OL,11,F"We believe that accountability and
OL,12,Fregulatory change must follow such a
OL,13,Fcatastrophic failure."
OL,15,FThey go on to hope the investigation's
OL,16,Fconclusion will lead to "meaningful
OL,17,Freform, rigorous safety standards, and
OL,18,Feffective oversight" in the
OL,19,Fsubmersible industry.
